<p source="SHANGBO.LUBANGDAHAN 2.6.1 (STRIP 1) JI XUSHENG 2: 42">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-1a.1">魯邦大旱,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-1a.2">哀公謂孔子:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-1a.3">「子不為我圖之?」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-1a.4">孔子對曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-1a.5">「邦大旱,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-1a.6">毋乃失諸刑與德乎?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-1a.7">唯 [...]</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.LUBANGDAHAN 2.6.2 (STRIP 2) JI XUSHENG 2: 42">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-2a.1">[...] 之何哉?」[...] why?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-2a.2">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-2a.3">「庶民知說之事鬼也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-2a.4">不知刑與德.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-2a.5">汝毋愛珪璧幣帛於山川,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-2a.6">正刑與〔德〕[...]</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.LUBANGDAHAN 2.6.3 (STRIPS 3-4) JI XUSHENG 2: 42">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-3a.1">[...] [孔子] 出,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-3a.2">遇子貢曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-3a.3">「賜, 爾聞巷路之言,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-3a.4">毋乃謂丘之對非歟?」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-3a.5">子貢曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-3a.6">「否,繄?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-3a.7">吾子若重命其歟?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-3a.8">若夫正刑與德,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-3a.9">以事上天,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-3a.10">此是哉.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-3a.11">若夫毋愛珪璧幣帛於山川,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-3a.12">毋乃不可.」</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.LUBANGDAHAN 2.6.4 (STRIP 4) JI XUSHENG 2: 42">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-4a.1">「夫山,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-4a.2">石以為膚,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-4a.3">木以為民,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-4a.4">如天不雨,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-4a.5">石將焦,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-4a.6">木將死,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-4a.7">其欲雨有甚於我,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-4a.8">又必待吾命乎?</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.LUBANGDAHAN 2.6.5 (STRIPS 4-5) JI XUSHENG 2: 42">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-5a.1">夫川,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-5a.2">水以為膚,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-5a.3">魚以為民,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-5a.4">如天不雨,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-5a.5">水將涸,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-5a.6">魚將死,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-5a.7">其欲雨有甚於我,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0037_tls_001-5a.8">又必待吾命乎?」</seg>
                </p>

